---
---

<section class="bg-white-glow py-16 md:py-24 px-5">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <p class="section-intro">
        lo que vas a encontrar
      </p>

      <h2 class="section-title text-text-deep">
        165 páginas para escribir tu historia.
      </h2>

      <p class="font-body text-base text-text-muted max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Cada bloque responde a una intención concreta: empezar desde <strong class="text-text-deep">quién eres hoy</strong>, explorar tu identidad, <strong class="text-text-deep">mirar tus vínculos</strong>, y <strong class="text-text-deep">celebrar lo que eres</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats bar -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-3 md:gap-6 mb-14 bg-lavender-mist/60 rounded-2xl p-5 md:p-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="block font-heading text-3xl md:text-5xl text-purple-vibrant leading-none">7</span>
        <span class="font-body text-xs md:text-sm text-text-muted mt-1 block">capítulos</span>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="block font-heading text-3xl md:text-5xl text-purple-vibrant leading-none">85+</span>
        <span class="font-body text-xs md:text-sm text-text-muted mt-1 block">ejercicios</span>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="block font-heading text-3xl md:text-5xl text-purple-vibrant leading-none">35</span>
        <span class="font-body text-xs md:text-sm text-text-muted mt-1 block">canciones</span>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="block font-heading text-3xl md:text-5xl text-purple-vibrant leading-none">165</span>
        <span class="font-body text-xs md:text-sm text-text-muted mt-1 block">páginas</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Chapters - real names from journal -->
    <div class="space-y-3 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-lavender-mist/40 border border-soft-lilac/40 hover:border-purple-heart/30 transition-colors duration-200">
        <span class="font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl text-purple-vibrant w-7 text-center shrink-0 leading-none mt-1">1</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-body font-bold text-text-deep text-sm md:text-base">Empieza aquí</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-xs md:text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Tu autorretrato, tu nombre, 20 cosas sobre ti. <strong class="text-text-deep">Quién eres hoy</strong>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-lavender-mist/40 border border-soft-lilac/40 hover:border-purple-heart/30 transition-colors duration-200">
        <span class="font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl text-purple-vibrant w-7 text-center shrink-0 leading-none mt-1">2</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-body font-bold text-text-deep text-sm md:text-base">"Love Yourself" — Explorando tu identidad individual</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-xs md:text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Sueños, trascendencia espiritual, mirarte a la cara y ser quien sos.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-lavender-mist/40 border border-soft-lilac/40 hover:border-purple-heart/30 transition-colors duration-200">
        <span class="font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl text-purple-vibrant w-7 text-center shrink-0 leading-none mt-1">3</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-body font-bold text-text-deep text-sm md:text-base">"You Never Walk Alone" — Tu identidad social</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-xs md:text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Brindo por mi familia, por mis amigos, por el amor. <strong class="text-text-deep">Cartas que necesitabas escribir</strong>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-lavender-mist/40 border border-soft-lilac/40 hover:border-purple-heart/30 transition-colors duration-200">
        <span class="font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl text-purple-vibrant w-7 text-center shrink-0 leading-none mt-1">4</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-body font-bold text-text-deep text-sm md:text-base">Tu biograma musical</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-xs md:text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">La huella de la música en tu historia personal. <strong class="text-text-deep">Canciones que te sostuvieron</strong>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-lavender-mist/40 border border-soft-lilac/40 hover:border-purple-heart/30 transition-colors duration-200">
        <span class="font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl text-purple-vibrant w-7 text-center shrink-0 leading-none mt-1">5</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-body font-bold text-text-deep text-sm md:text-base">Soy parte de un poderoso fandom llamado ARMY</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-xs md:text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Tu conexión con el fandom, lo que significa pertenecer a algo más grande.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-lavender-mist/40 border border-soft-lilac/40 hover:border-purple-heart/30 transition-colors duration-200">
        <span class="font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl text-purple-vibrant w-7 text-center shrink-0 leading-none mt-1">6</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-body font-bold text-text-deep text-sm md:text-base">La celebración de quien soy</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-xs md:text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Promesas contigo misma, cartas al futuro. <strong class="text-text-deep">Celebrar todo lo que eres</strong>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-lavender-mist/40 border border-soft-lilac/40 hover:border-purple-heart/30 transition-colors duration-200">
        <span class="font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl text-purple-vibrant w-7 text-center shrink-0 leading-none mt-1">7</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-body font-bold text-text-deep text-sm md:text-base">Fandom Art Space</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-xs md:text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Espacios de creación libre para expresarte sin límites.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
